1
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:43,600
Look at this face.

2
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:45,100
Is it familiar?

3
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,440
Aren't you...

4
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,160
Why are you here?

5
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:51,200
And you said you didn't know.

6
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:53,320
Tell me.

7
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:54,800
What is the truth about what happened back then?

8
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:55,160
Stop.

9
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:59,080
My name is Feifei.

10
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:01,240
I am Mr. Angwei's secretary.

11
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:03,920
There are many people who look alike.

12
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:05,920
It's not surprising you mistook me.

13
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,080
Young Master Ang Wei.

14
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:09,960
I swear to God.

15
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,240
I really don't know about this.

16
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,280
It has nothing to do with me.

17
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,680
Please spare me, Young Master Ang Wei.

18
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:15,080
You deny it quite fast.

19
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,640
What if your identity

20
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:21,640
is fake to begin with?

21
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:25,800
Miss Feifei.

22
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,600
Why don't you teach me

23
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:31,000
how to make him understand

24
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,680
the meaning of loyalty?

25
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:37,479
How would I know?

26
00:01:37,479 --> 00:01:38,340
You don't know?

27
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,320
Then let me teach you.

28
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,320
Only bullets

29
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,690
can make them remember things.

30
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:51,280
Shoot.

31
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,960
And I will believe you are not Dai Ling.

32
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:54,680
After all, Dai Ling

33
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,680
wouldn't even dare to step on an ant.

34
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,720
Miss Feifei.

35
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,620
I beg you, please don't shoot.

36
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,560
My wife is still waiting for me

37
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,920
to have dinner.

38
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:10,080
I also have a three-year-old child.

39
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,400
He can't even speak yet.

40
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,640
Shoot.

41
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,560
I beg you.

42
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:17,040
Help me punish this disloyal servant.

43
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:19,280
Miss Feifei.

44
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:21,040
Shoot.

45
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,520
He is testing my identity.

46
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,960
He wants me to panic.

47
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,440
I absolutely cannot expose myself.

48
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,400
Shoot.

49
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:32,280
Shoot, and I'll believe you're not Dai Ling.

50
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,160
Shoot.

51
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,520
Shoot.

52
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,400
I'll bet on it.

53
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,160
You played me.

54
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,920
Young Master Ang Wei uses murder to prove

55
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,450
whether I am Dai Ling or not.

56
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,720
I can't believe you came up with this.

57
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,480
Do you miss her too much?

58
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,960
You hope I am her so much.

59
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,320
So you use such a ridiculous reason

60
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,040
to test me.

61
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,720
You said Dai Ling is a coward.

62
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:12,500
Then when you pushed her into the sea,

63
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,000
did she, like just now,

64
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,120
cry and beg you

65
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,640
to save her?

66
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,640
So gutsy.

67
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,720
Aren't you afraid I'll kill you?

68
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,240
I look so much like her.

69
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,079
Could you bear it?

70
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,400
Don't you like to gamble?

71
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,120
Then let's make a bet.

72
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:44,000
Bet that you will fall madly in love with me.

73
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,480
Old friends meeting.

74
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:58,570
There's no need to be at each other's throats.

75
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,360
Ou Shaowen.

76
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,160
Why is it you again?

77
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:08,480
Don't ruin my mood.

78
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,850
I'm not here to make trouble this time.

79
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,240
I want to tell you something.

80
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,839
When some people are gone, they are truly gone.

81
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,320
She is Feifei.

82
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,050
Not Dai Ling.

83
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:31,080
You say, the crimes some people committed five years ago,

84
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:34,130
do they have to come back five years later?

85
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:48,920
Dailing.

86
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,680
I never thought

87
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,810
of pushing you down.

88
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:58,880
Dailing.

89
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,840
Dailing.

90
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:46,250
Are you looking for me, Master Angwei?

91
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,000
Does this look familiar?

92
00:05:58,760 --> 00:06:01,290
This river connects Mancheng and Biancheng.

93
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,930
Of course I'm familiar with it.

94
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,080
Is that so?

95
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:18,890
Then don't blame me.

96
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,530
Did you bring me here

97
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,720
expecting me to act like the old Dailing

98
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,260
and hold onto your arm crying?

99
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,730
Do you remember this river?

100
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:05,920
Five years ago,

101
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,920
it was right here.

102
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,020
Are you scared?

103
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,600
Not at all.

104
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,980
Master Angwei,

105
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,540
you can try letting go.

106
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,800
I died here once.

107
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,570
How could I be afraid of you?

108
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,640
Why does it seem like

109
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:49,409
Master Angwei is the one who's afraid?

110
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:57,960
Angwei.

111
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,520
Did you know

112
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,940
that the flames of revenge

113
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:07,640
have long surpassed the fear of death?

114
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,610
Is Master Angwei

115
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,559
remembering Dailing?

116
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,370
Even if you do what you just did,

117
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,799
push me down a hundred times,

118
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,360
or pull me up a hundred times,

119
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,160
she's already dead.

120
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:51,760
Isn't it?

121
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,040
Who gave you the nerve to say that?

122
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,330
Aren't you afraid of death?

123
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,980
That's not what I'm afraid of.

124
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,000
Look closely.

125
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:18,640
My name is Feifei,

126
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,080
not Dailing.

127
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:28,960
Dailing.

128
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,280
I know

129
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:33,260
you came back to get revenge on me.

130
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:36,480
Feifei.

131
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:40,560
Tomorrow, Danpa is hosting a banquet at Haihu Manor.

132
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:42,760
Many big names in Mancheng will attend.

133
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:45,120
I wonder if I have the honor

134
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:47,210
of inviting you to be my date

135
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,810
to attend together.

136
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,960
It's very kind of you, Mr. Ou.

137
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,600
But I just signed

138
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,730
a three-month agreement with Angwei.

139
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:58,120
I will be his personal secretary for these three months.

140
00:09:58,120 --> 00:10:01,650
He doesn't allow me to have any alone time with the opposite sex.

141
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:04,610
Not allowed to have alone time with the opposite sex.

142
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:07,420
Indeed, only a guy like Angwei

143
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,970
could come up with such a ridiculous idea.

144
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,560
However, many important people at tomorrow's banquet

145
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:16,420
have had decades of friendship with the Dai family.

146
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,080
For example,

147
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,120
Lapeng.

148
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,200
Mom.

149
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,640
Dailing,

150
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,650
leave me alone, just go.

151
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,640
Run.

152
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:36,080
Run.

153
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:39,280
Run.

154
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,130
Have you heard of it?

155
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,920
I really haven't heard of it.

156
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,560
But why

157
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:54,360
pay attention to those closely associated with the Dai family?

158
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:56,420
Could it be that you, Young Master Ou,

159
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:58,320
are very interested in the past affairs of the Dai family?

160
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:00,560
What happened to the Dai family back then is indeed suspicious.

161
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:01,480
But rather than saying

162
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:03,940
I'm interested in the Dai family's affairs,

163
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,800
it's more that I want to know

164
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:09,810
what exactly happened five years ago.

165
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:20,760
Tomorrow at 7:00 p.m.,

166
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:21,490
Haihu Manor.

167
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,880
See you there.

168
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,680
Lapeng,

169
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,920
the enemy who burned my mother to death.

170
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:34,680
Even if this banquet is a dragon's den,

171
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,960
I will go and take his life myself.
